http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/bangalore/Cab-driver-beaten-to-death/article14005194.ece

A 31-year old cab driver was allegedly beaten to death at Ganganagar in the early hours of Monday. The police suspect a gang of four murdered him.Police sources identified the victim, Arun, who was passing through Gangenahalli locality when he was attacked by the gang. RT Nagar police recovered the body following a preliminary investigation and have launched a hunt for the killers.